yments network for freight by thinking like a bank, operating like a fintech, and refusing to do anything halfway.]]></description><link>https://thesilkroadnexus.substack.com/p/interview-with-aaron-graft-ceo-of</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://thesilkroadnexus.substack.com/p/interview-with-aaron-graft-ceo-of</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Nikhil Varshney]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Tue, 05 May 2026 14:02:47 GMT</pubDate><enclosure url="https://api.substack.com/feed/podcast/196506673/e2376aed26915830bf44b434cc206d7f.mp3" length="0" type="audio/mpeg"/><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Aaron Graft did not grow up thinking about trucking. He went from law school to distressed loan workouts, then bought distressed debt, then bought a distressed bank. That bank became the foundation for a freight payments network that today touches 70 percent of all loads in brokered freight and moves a couple of hundred million dollars a day.</p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2 is-viewable-img" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!YZJ_!,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff3e36478-2f51-46f7-8a8a-103bacd8c226_2729x1051.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!YZJ_!,w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff3e36478-2f51-46f7-8a8a-103bacd8c226_2729x1051.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!YZJ_!,w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff3e36478-2f51-46f7-8a8a-103bacd8c226_2729x1051.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!YZJ_!,w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff3e36478-2f51-46f7-8a8a-103bacd8c226_2729x1051.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!YZJ_!,w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff3e36478-2f51-46f7-8a8a-103bacd8c226_2729x1051.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!YZJ_!,w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff3e36478-2f51-46f7-8a8a-103bacd8c226_2729x1051.png" width="2729" height="1051" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/f3e36478-2f51-46f7-8a8a-103bacd8c226_2729x1051.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:1051,&quot;width&quot;:2729,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:2711357,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:true,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:&quot;https://thesilkroadnexus.substack.com/i/196506673?img=https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0e2685ae-233d-46c2-8bda-2de81e116916_2752x1536.png&quot;,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false,&quot;align&quot;:null,&quot;offset&quot;:false}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!YZJ_!,w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff3e36478-2f51-46f7-8a8a-103bacd8c226_2729x1051.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!YZJ_!,w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff3e36478-2f51-46f7-8a8a-103bacd8c226_2729x1051.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!YZJ_!,w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff3e36478-2f51-46f7-8a8a-103bacd8c226_2729x1051.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!YZJ_!,w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff3e36478-2f51-46f7-8a8a-103bacd8c226_2729x1051.png 1456w" sizes="100vw" fetchpriority="high"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><div class="pencraft pc-display-flex pc-gap-8 pc-reset"><button tabindex="0" type="button" class="pencraft pc-reset pencraft icon-container restack-image"><svg role="img" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="var(--color-fg-primary)" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><g><title></title><path d="M2.53001 7.81595C3.49179 4.73911 6.43281 2.5 9.91173 2.5C13.1684 2.5 15.9537 4.46214 17.0852 7.23684L17.6179 8.67647M17.6179 8.67647L18.5002 4.26471M17.6179 8.67647L13.6473 6.91176M17.4995 12.1841C16.5378 15.2609 13.5967 17.5 10.1178 17.5C6.86118 17.5 4.07589 15.5379 2.94432 12.7632L2.41165 11.3235M2.41165 11.3235L1.5293 15.7353M2.41165 11.3235L6.38224 13.0882"></path></g></svg></button><button tabindex="0" type="button" class="pencraft pc-reset pencraft icon-container view-image"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 lucide-maximize-2"><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></button></div></div></div></a></figure></div><p>Aaron Graft&#8217;s unconventional path from law to freight payments.</p><h2><strong>The Bank as a Structural Advantage</strong></h2><p>Graft offers a one-sentence definition of banking: banks buy money from depositors and sell money to borrowers. Small trucking companies haul freight for multi-billion dollar shippers, then wait 30 or more days to get paid. That timing gap is the entire market opportunity. Being a bank provides a lower cost of funds and the institutional capacity to serve both sides of the transaction. The charter was not just a regulatory artifact. It was an architectural advantage.</p><h2><strong>Three Ways a Trucker Gets Working Capital</strong></h2><p>Before factoring scaled in trucking, a small carrier had limited options: pay high rates to a payday lender, negotiate a quick-pay discount and accept less money, or factor invoices. Modern factoring has evolved well beyond financing into an outsourced back office and purchasing consortium. The value proposition shifted from &#8220;I need cash now&#8221; to &#8220;I need a business companion.&#8221;</p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2 is-viewable-img" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!63b1!,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F685c129c-2655-4cd5-99a3-028ea73d09a5_2752x1536.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!63b1!,w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F685c129c-2655-4cd5-99a3-028ea73d09a5_2752x1536.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!63b1!,w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F685c129c-2655-4cd5-99a3-028ea73d09a5_2752x1536.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!63b1!,w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F685c129c-2655-4cd5-99a3-028ea73d09a5_2752x1536.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!63b1!,w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F685c129c-2655-4cd5-99a3-028ea73d09a5_2752x1536.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!63b1!,w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F685c129c-2655-4cd5-99a3-028ea73d09a5_2752x1536.png" width="2752" height="1536" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/685c129c-2655-4cd5-99a3-028ea73d09a5_2752x1536.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:1536,&quot;width&quot;:2752,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:3915213,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:&quot;https://thesilkroadnexus.substack.com/i/196506673?img=https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F2bc50c07-9411-40e5-bf05-9c4371e2dc65_2752x1536.png&quot;,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false,&quot;align&quot;:null,&quot;offset&quot;:false}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!63b1!,w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F685c129c-2655-4cd5-99a3-028ea73d09a5_2752x1536.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!63b1!,w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F685c129c-2655-4cd5-99a3-028ea73d09a5_2752x1536.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!63b1!,w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F685c129c-2655-4cd5-99a3-028ea73d09a5_2752x1536.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!63b1!,w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F685c129c-2655-4cd5-99a3-028ea73d09a5_2752x1536.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><div class="pencraft pc-display-flex pc-gap-8 pc-reset"><button tabindex="0" type="button" class="pencraft pc-reset pencraft icon-container restack-image"><svg role="img" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="var(--color-fg-primary)" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><g><title></title><path d="M2.53001 7.81595C3.49179 4.73911 6.43281 2.5 9.91173 2.5C13.1684 2.5 15.9537 4.46214 17.0852 7.23684L17.6179 8.67647M17.6179 8.67647L18.5002 4.26471M17.6179 8.67647L13.6473 6.91176M17.4995 12.1841C16.5378 15.2609 13.5967 17.5 10.1178 17.5C6.86118 17.5 4.07589 15.5379 2.94432 12.7632L2.41165 11.3235M2.41165 11.3235L1.5293 15.7353M2.41165 11.3235L6.38224 13.0882"></path></g></svg></button><button tabindex="0" type="button" class="pencraft pc-reset pencraft icon-container view-image"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 lucide-maximize-2"><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></button></div></div></div></a></figure></div><p>The three paths to working capital for small carriers.</p><h2><strong>The 80/20 of Fraud</strong></h2><p>Across roughly $100 billion in purchased invoices, 80 percent of Triumph&#8217;s risk comes from fraud, not from the debtor&#8217;s inability to pay. The fraud is straightforward: the truck simply never moved. The invoice is fiction. The challenge is underwriting $1,500 invoices and funding them in under an hour. Half-measures kill you in factoring. You need the full ecosystem running continuously in the background.</p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2 is-viewable-img" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!5Ohx!,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb3973fe9-ed83-4563-8673-492e948df92e_2752x1536.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!5Ohx!,w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb3973fe9-ed83-4563-8673-492e948df92e_2752x1536.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!5Ohx!,w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb3973fe9-ed83-4563-8673-492e948df92e_2752x1536.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!5Ohx!,w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb3973fe9-ed83-4563-8673-492e948df92e_2752x1536.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!5Ohx!,w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb3973fe9-ed83-4563-8673-492e948df92e_2752x1536.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!5Ohx!,w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb3973fe9-ed83-4563-8673-492e948df92e_2752x1536.png" width="2752" height="1536" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/b3973fe9-ed83-4563-8673-492e948df92e_2752x1536.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:1536,&quot;width&quot;:2752,&quot