c95aac3b_2560x362.png 1456w" sizes="100vw" fetchpriority="high"></picture><div></div></div></a></figure></div><p>Amazon commerce business has made tremendous progress in the last two years. North America operating income hit $8.3 billion in a single quarter, up 42% year over year. International turned a $1.4 billion operating profit. Combined Stores operating income was $9.7 billion for the quarter, on pace for nearly $40 billion annualized.</p><p>To appreciate how dramatic the transformation is: as recently as 2022, the North America segment was losing money. Three years later, it is generating margins approaching 8% and accelerating. The International segment, which was burning billions annually, has now been profitable for six consecutive quarters.</p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2 is-viewable-img" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!4TlY!,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F310922c9-cea6-4293-bc65-06d043e6f0ce_2580x880.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!4TlY!,w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F310922c9-cea6-4293-bc65-06d043e6f0ce_2580x880.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!4TlY!,w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F310922c9-cea6-4293-bc65-06d043e6f0ce_2580x880.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!4TlY!,w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F310922c9-cea6-4293-bc65-06d043e6f0ce_2580x880.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!4TlY!,w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-pos